tool_description:
Profile CSV files with pandas profiling. You can create Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) with this endpoint.

Please bear in mind that creating HTML report may take time up to 10 seconds!

Maximum file size: 75 Kb
Accepted File Type: .csv

If you need to profile bigger sized files, you can check www.sweephy.com
